{"tid":970814,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【大學宿舍好淫亂】1男2女同床啜啜聲","createTime":"2019-01-06T06:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T07:36:13.000Z","uid":41992,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3afa30ed121df8a2a15fb39677f425d32336dd72","tid":970814,"uid":41992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:57:46.000Z","msg":"這一代的大學生，性觀念開放了很多。一名恒大畢業生，向本刊說出了她在宿舍看到的荒淫事&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.<br />\n<br />\n「覺得佢哋將宿舍當咗炮房！」Rainbow（化名）為香港恒生大學畢業生，在學期間曾經居住學校宿舍。她表示，曾與一班女同學於房間內飲酒談心，期間有人帶同兩名異性加入，有女生突然表示「好暈、好醉、好唔舒服！」其後女生步入房內洗手間「作嘔」，眾人打算關心她之際，被眼前畫面震懾。「打開洗手間門，見到佢同個男仔攬住咗！」<br />\n<br />\n在酒精作用之下，加上情到濃時，年輕人難免按捺不住內心的情慾。然而，事情並非單純男歡女愛。「大家都覺得好震驚，因為男、女事主有各自嘅男女朋友。」<br />\n<br />\n新一代思想前衛，性觀念開放，即使有另一半，不少人亦有SP（即Sex Partner性伴侶）。一人滿足心理需要，另一人滿足生理需要，各司其職，解決情感所需。<br />\n<br />\n眾人不以為然，繼續把酒言歡，其後大家睡意漸濃決定休息，豈料&hellip;&hellip;「當時一名女生與洗手間男事主正睡在其中一張床上，但忽然聽到洗手間女事主爬上佢哋張床！」她憶述，當時已關上燈準備休息，沒有人知道發生什麼事，黑暗中卻傳來一輪熱吻及撥弄東西的聲音&hellip;&hellip;「直到就快天光嘅時候，男、女事主一齊返左女事主間房。」<br />\n<br />\n本刊就事件向涉事學校查詢，香港恒生大學回應指，學校住宿書院屬男女分層，宿生出入書院需經過認證方可進出。宿生朋友可在指定訪客探訪時間內到訪（上午8:00至同日晚上11:00），惟校方強調，宿生不得在非探訪時間內進入異性樓層或異性房間。"},{"pid":"e9389c8969c98679a24c8eb66a2a6362147f8ffc","tid":970814,"uid":41992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:58:22.000Z","msg":"桓大世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec3de60def11228129352e7a98d39d6d73de2f9","tid":970814,"uid":41992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:59:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20190106/2_647876_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190106%2F2_647876_0&d=X4%2FzfWi5cbJ7qy%2BCoL4Pzf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=a2ef3f26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190106%2F2_647876_0&h=fc992134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20190106/2_647876_0</a>"},{"pid":"57060b7bff3bdc30535cbbcc9544675a4243e060","tid":970814,"uid":64374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:01:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64bbfac5797b013571ebb4cfd9d6cd2f6c9bc6ee","tid":970814,"uid":191352,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:02:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cb554127a36a845bf753e3be2c2ae301c13e7a9","tid":970814,"uid":219183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:02:19.000Z","msg":"抄人好好玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45c6ffb6ca11d06dbff5515711563d039a7c651","tid":970814,"uid":219183,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2cb554127a36a845bf753e3be2c2ae301c13e7a9","tid":970814,"uid":219183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:02:19.000Z","msg":"抄人好好玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:02:56.000Z","msg":"利申：禾含"},{"pid":"66361aea7459612f6f5444b13deb0b69073b4cda","tid":970814,"uid":41992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cb554127a36a845bf753e3be2c2ae301c13e7a9","tid":970814,"uid":219183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:02:19.000Z","msg":"抄人好好玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:03:00.000Z","msg":"梳 冇留意到人有巴打開左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781f8d04528209a4ebc29d3b3f7ce4fb70357da7","tid":970814,"uid":201834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"